ets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有個досто, 唔特登查字典，俄羅斯人都唔知係乜"},{"pid":"8ecab74410d3c9d9b1865e6b0514ba0ae4201397","tid":85763,"uid":75612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n仲有d字好撚長, 屌佢老母臭西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德文笑而不語</blockquote><br />\non9 我肯定咁話比你聽德文字長得黎極易拆<br />\n俄文冇得拆，難好多<br />\n利申：德文C1／2, 俄文B1</blockquote><br />\n德文你邊度學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144ae740c86511d2711d91f3500a90dab8d3d64b","tid":85763,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Привет. Рад познакомиться с русскоговорящими гонконгцыми. Как дела?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nПривет братик. Я узнаю твое имя но уже забыл где я тебя видел <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nТы учусь в настоящее время в языковой школе в России да?"},{"pid":"6742889a9aac16c58ffe1960edb78a2c7ca79b0b","tid":85763,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n仲有d字好撚長, 屌佢老母臭西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德文笑而不語</blockquote><br />\non9 我肯定咁話比你聽德文字長得黎極易拆<br />\n俄文冇得拆，難好多<br />\n利申：德文C1／2, 俄文B1</blockquote><br />\n德文你邊度學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柏林某大學，跟住某小城市大學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d31ff91f9156793edd71e886a5d1146516f13ca","tid":85763,"uid":30642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"Cyka Blyat"},{"pid":"63dd678d927c96fd880e790a437dafcfedad2790","tid":85763,"uid":74151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r